{
  "stem": "8002.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they used to call you dirty Jew.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You're too lazy.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You don't like to work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You like to do a lot of business.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But you don't like to work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we told them, we were only students not trying to be better than anybody else, just studying.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they didn't like it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They-- they say we're too smart.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, during play.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "During play.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not really.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Verbal.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not my friends, no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were good friends.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We lived in-- we had an apartment house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In Viski, we lived in a house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had-- we had like a ranch house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And, of course, there was no street, because it was a small town.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And everything was fine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when we moved to Dvinsk, my father bought a big apartment house.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were living downstairs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we had tenants.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we had-- we had our own rooms.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had a study room.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had a big dining room.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had a table.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You could sit 12 people, like a conference room.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course, Rosh Hashanna, Yom Kippur, [NON-ENGLISH], [NON-ENGLISH], [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] [NON-ENGLISH], [NON-ENGLISH], and Purim, the most happiest [NON-ENGLISH]",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we had-- oh, we used to have at least-- every time we had a Passover, we had about 30, 40 people for the Seder.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some relatives, some neighbors, some friends.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, first, it was covered with table cloth, beautiful linen table cloth.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All the forks, knives, and everything was silver, gold plated.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the plate was from China.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think it was Rosenthal china.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, of course, Passover was when everything was displayed, the most expensive articles.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
